node.text:
The Peacock bite was on fire today! Caught 16 in one hour, along with a 5lb Largemouth Bass & a Mayan Cichlid! Caught one of my hook-ups on video with my phone in my shorts 🤣 Too much fun!
#peacock #bass #peacockbass #crotchcam #freshwaterfishing #freshwater #bassfishing

node.text:
Spent 6 days fishing offshore in Panama at @tropicstarlodge! Caught 10 Black Marlin, my biggest being just under 500 pounds which was tagged & released by Guy Harvey and his team, along with numerous 30+ pound Dorado, some nice Yellowfin Tuna, Pacific Sailfish, Shark and more! Check out some highlights of my adventure! 
@pelagicgear // @pelagicgirl

node.text:
Birthday 𝙏𝙍𝙄𝙋! Went out to catch a Sword with friends & came across some small weed patches. Sight-casted a bunch of Mahi along with this Triple Tail I caught and released. Fun day with great friends! As for the swordfish, we hooked a nice one on our last drift of the day, but it pulled hook 3/4 of the way up. 😏 Until next time..
#birthdaygirl #tripletail #trip #mahimahi #dolphinfish #workandplay #catchandrelease #swordfish #deepdrop

node.text:
Happy Independence Day weekend, my friends!! 🇺🇸 Just a friendly little reminder from the @ridedrydrivedry team, the USCG and me to be safe this weekend on the water while celebrating [the best country on Earth!!!! 🇺🇸❤️🙌🏽] Always, always make sure to have a Sober Captain and please also  spread the word to your friends and family! 🙏
@uscg #4thofjuly #independenceday #usa #america #ilovemycountry #patriot
